  "body": "I want to build decentralized system. So I have a system where users can generate address by one click than recieve coins (ETH,BTC,LTC) and get bonuses. So to have a security system I built a watch-only wallet for BTC,LTC -(in my local machine I installed Electrum-BTC and Electrum-LTC , than have took from there xpub key and in my online service I am genereting addresses for users). But on ETH there is no way to make concept look like this. Can you give me a good solution for the Ethereum? How can I make watch only wallet which will generate addreses for users, check transactions and balances but no one could send from there.\r\nThanks!",
